data.description: 'Dream Ridge Cabin' is located in the Hidden Mountain Resort close to all the things you love to do in the Great Smoky Mountains! Turn key, rent ready!!  Well appointed & tastefully decorated, this contemporary rustic cabin has all the modern conveniences!  Soaring cathedral ceiling! This fully furnished cabin boasts new flooring, new oversized soaking tub, new stove, new washer & dryer, new bunk beds, new double reclining sofa, new table & chairs and new toilet in the bathroom! This cozy cabin will sleep up to 6 people comfortably! Neat & clean & turn key ready!  220 wiring on the front covered porch will accommodate a hot tub.  The HVAC has been recently replaced with a new 3 ton unit in 2019. Owners enjoy the many amenities within the resort such as: gated resort, pool, event space /club house, gazebo, fishing ponds, picnic areas,   on site management for overnight guest accommodations.  'Dream Ridge Cabin' is an comfortable place to call home, second home or a perfect opportunity to own your very own investment cabin in the Smokies! Dollywood, Tanger Five Oaks Shopping Mall, Pigeon Forge, Gatlinburg, Dolly's Stampede Dinner Show, Skyland Ranch & the Great Smoky Mountain National Park are just minutes away for all your enjoyment!
